D. and Kaprio, Jaakko and Medland, Sarah E. and Walters, Robin G. and Benjamin, Daniel J. and Turley, Patrick and Evans, David M. and Davey Smith, George and Hayward, Caroline and Brumpton, Ben and Hemani, Gibran and Davies, Neil M.},
