}

@online{tan2024-fgwas,
  title = {Family-{{GWAS}} Reveals Effects of Environment and Mating on Genetic Associations},
  author = {Tan, Tammy and Jayashankar, Hariharan and Guan, Junming and Nehzati, Seyed Moeen and Mir, Mahdi and Bennett, Michael and Agerbo, Esben and Ahlskog, Rafael and Anapaz, Ville Pinto de Andrade and Åsvold, Bjørn Olav and Benonisdottir, Stefania and Bhatta, Laxmi and Boomsma, Dorret I. and Brumpton, Ben and Campbell, Archie and Chabris, Christopher F. and Cheesman, Rosa and Chen, Zhengming and Group, China Kadoorie Biobank Collaborative and family=Geus, given=Eco, prefix=de, useprefix=false and Ehli, Erik A. and Elnahas, Abdelrahman G. and Team, Estonian Biobank Research and Finngen and Ganna, Andrea and Giannelis, Alexandros and Hakaste, Liisa and Hansen, Ailin Falkmo and Havdahl, Alexandra and Hayward, Caroline and Hottenga, Jouke-Jan and Houmark, Mikkel Aagaard and Hveem, Kristian and Kaprio, Jaakko and Langhammer, Arnulf and Latvala, Antti and Lee, James J. and Lehtovirta, Mikko and Li, Liming and Study, LifeLines Cohort and Lin, Kuang and Linnér, Richard Karlsson and Lombardi, Stefano and Martin, Nicholas G. and McGue, Matt and Medland, Sarah E. and Metspalu, Andres and Mitchell, Brittany L. and Ni, Guiyan and Nolte, Ilja M. and Oetjens, Matthew T. and Oskarsson, Sven and Palviainen, Teemu and Prasad, Rashmi B. and Reigo, Anu and Reis, Kadri and Sidorenko, Julia and Silventoinen, Karri and Snieder, Harold and Tuomi, Tiinamaija and Vilhjálmsson, Bjarni J. and Walters, Robin G. and Willoughby, Emily A. and Winsvold, Bendik S. and Ystrom, Eivind and Flint, Jonathan and Yengo, Loic and Visscher, Peter M. and Kong, Augustine and Tucker-Drob, Elliot M. and Border, Richard and Cesarini, David and Turley, Patrick and Okbay, Aysu and Benjamin, Daniel J. and Young, Alexander Strudwick},
  date = {2024-10-04},
